### Create a new Category
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/categories
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Beverages",
  "slug": "beverages",
  "imageUrl": "https://example.com/images/beverages.png",
  "sortOrder": 1,
  "isActive": true,
  "description": "All kinds of drinks and beverages"
}

###

### Get all Categories
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/categories
Accept: application/json

###

### Get Categories Paginated
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/categories/page?page=0&size=5
Accept: application/json

###

### Get a single Category by ID (Replace 1 with actual ID)
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/categories/1
Accept: application/json

###

### Update a Category (Replace 1 with actual ID)
PUT http://localhost:8080/api/v1/categories/1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Beverages (Updated)",
  "slug": "beverages-updated",
  "imageUrl": "https://example.com/images/beverages-new.png",
  "sortOrder": 2,
  "isActive": true,
  "description": "Updated description for beverages"
}

###

### Delete a Category (Replace 1 with actual ID)
DELETE http://localhost:8080/api/v1/categories/1
Accept: application/json
